snippet.title: SPY X FAMILY ED1 喜劇 "KIGEKI" (Anya's Fun Cover)
snippet.description:
Who's excited to see Spy X Family on the screen? I can't wait to sit down with a cuppa and chill to this! The original ED is amazing, and so I thought I would re-create it in Anya Forger's version! P/S I love both peanuts and carrots. 

Arrangement, Instrumental, Vocals, Audio and Video production - JustCosplaySings
